title.es: I just sat down. Already regret it.
title.pt-BR: Cold food again. Right on schedule.

comment.en: Their simple motivations always make me question my own complex struggles.
comment.es: Su simpleza siempre me hace dudar de mis líos.
comment.pt-BR: A simplicidade deles me faz duvidar do meu drama.

title.en: Why do I even bother, the food's cold already.
title.pt-BR: Sitting down. For five seconds, maybe.

comment.en: It's humbling how much simpler animal instinct seems compared to my daily lesson plans.
comment.es: Qué simple el instinto animal. Y yo con mis lecciones...
comment.pt-BR: Que simplicidade animal... Meus planos, então.

title.en: My food's cold again. Of course.
title.pt-BR: Past quitting time. Why am I still here?

comment.en: I mostly just wish I had their natural talent for resting.
comment.es: Ojalá tuviera su don para el descanso.
comment.pt-BR: Queria o dom deles de descansar.

title.pt-BR: Sat down. Knew I'd regret it.

comment.en: Patience is certainly a virtue; one I am constantly reminded I should cultivate more.
comment.es: La paciencia es una virtud que, parece, me falta.
comment.pt-BR: Paciência, uma virtude que me lembram sempre.

title.en: Sitting down. My back already hurts.
title.es: My food's getting cold again, of course.
title.pt-BR: My food's cold again. Guess I earned it.

comment.en: One always tries their best, yet the universe often offers its own unique curriculum.
comment.es: Uno hace lo que puede; la vida, sus otras clases.
comment.pt-BR: A gente se esforça. O universo? Tem outro curso.

title.en: My ass hit the chair. It rang. Of course.

comment.en: It's remarkable how some creatures just know what they're doing, unlike me.
comment.es: Qué bien algunos saben qué hacen. Uno, no.
comment.pt-BR: Bichos se viram. Só eu que não.
